From 64bb9b06fa7ee463aae6cd192dc3056ecf031f87 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ivan Khokhlov <ivan.s.khokhlov@rt.ru>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 00:24:18 +0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] winemac: fall back to offscreen views for pbuffers

Keep using real CGL pbuffers when they can be created, but fall back
to an NSView-backed offscreen drawable when CGLCreatePBuffer() fails.

Teach the render-to-texture fallback path to redirect glCopyTexImage2D
and glCopyTexSubImage2D through readback and upload when the drawable is
view-backed, and preserve viewport/scissor state while switching into
the emulated drawable.

Observed while debugging World of Warcraft 3.3.5a indoor minimap
rendering on Apple Silicon macOS.
